OL,3,CHomes evacuated in Shropshire village
OL,4,Cafter suspected explosive device found
OL,6,FA number of homes in the village of in
OL,7,FLeegomery in Shropshire were evacuated
OL,8,Fon Tuesday night (3 March) after
OL,9,Fpolice discovered a suspected
OL,10,Fexplosive device.
OL,12,FWest Mercia Police officers were
OL,13,Fcalled to a property in Saxon Court
OL,14,Fwhere they found the device and nearby
OL,15,Fhomes were evacuated as a precaution.
