OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772637082
OL,3,CHomes evacuated in Shropshire village
OL,4,Cafter suspected explosive device found
OL,6,FIn a statement Telford & Wrekin Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "An 100m cordon is now in place
OL,8,Fand surrounding homes have been
OL,9,Fevacuated as a precaution. The
OL,10,FExplosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD) Team
OL,11,Fhave been called to the scene to make
OL,12,Fa full assessment.
OL,14,F"Officers are asking people to please
OL,15,Favoid the immediate area. They will
OL,16,Fkeep the impacted residents informed
OL,17,Fas the incident progresses.
OL,19,F"We will provide more information once
OL,20,Fwe are able to do so."
